Node.SubjRefEnglish: {beast of bird of every fishes of}

Node.Notes: Uncertain. Assumes: from the hand of humans, [i.e.,] from the hand of a human, [i.e.,] one’s fellow, I will seek an accounting for the life of humans.
Dislocated np: "The one shedding human blood, by a human his blood will be shed."
Carries over "I will establish my covenant" from previous verse.

Exact grouping of creatures uncertain. Tree assumes "all the living creatures that [are] with you among the birds, among the livestock, and among all the wild animals of the earth with you, from all coming out of the ark to every creature of the earth."
